OL,3,CPrawn cocktails and pavlova back on
OL,4,Cmenu as 1980s revival boosts demand
OL,6,FA surge in demand for food from the
OL,7,F1980s is sweeping supermarkets and
OL,8,Frestaurants alike, as one grocer
OL,9,Flaunches a guide to throwing the
OL,10,Fperfect '80s dinner party.
OL,12,FThe craze, thought to be driven at
OL,13,Fleast in part by the return of Jilly
OL,14,FCooper's Rivals series to TV screens,
OL,15,Fhas led to Waitrose reporting soaring
OL,16,Fsales of tiramisu and corned beef,
OL,17,Fwhile chef Gordon Ramsay's restaurants
OL,18,Fhave added pavlova and a twist on rum
OL,19,Fbaba to their menus.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
