OL,3,CPrawn cocktails and pavlova back on
OL,4,Cmenu as 1980s revival boosts demand
OL,6,FAlmost half of UK adults (48%) say
OL,7,F1980s dishes are making a comeback,
OL,8,Faccording to a survey for Waitrose.
OL,10,FSome 28% said prawn cocktail was the
OL,11,Fdish they most wanted to see back on
OL,12,Ftheir tables, followed by beef
OL,13,Fbourguignon (24%) and bread and butter
OL,14,Fpudding (24%).
OL,16,FA fifth (20%) mentioned rhubarb and
OL,17,Fcustard, 19% said they would enjoy a
OL,18,Fbanana split and 18% said they would
OL,19,Fenjoy a quiche Lorraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
