PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781385841
OL,3,CPrawn cocktails and pavlova back on
OL,4,Cmenu as 1980s revival boosts demand
OL,6,FThe grocer said sales of its luxury
OL,7,Fprawn cocktail had jumped 170% year on
OL,8,Fyear, while apple tarte tatin was up
OL,9,F104%.
OL,11,FLondon stalwart The Savoy Grill said
OL,12,Ftarte tatin was now one of its most
OL,13,Fpopular choices, while head chef
OL,14,FArnaud Stevens is introducing the
OL,15,Fmojito baba to the menu ` a twist on
OL,16,Fthe 1980s classic rum baba and
OL,17,Ffeaturing a light baba sponge, lime
OL,18,Fand mint syrup and lemon curd.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
