PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781385841
OL,3,CPrawn cocktails and pavlova back on
OL,4,Cmenu as 1980s revival boosts demand
OL,6,FWaitrose has even launched a 1980s
OL,7,Fdinner party guide, describing it as a
OL,8,F"celebration of the decade's most
OL,9,Ficonic food" and providing guidance on
OL,10,Fformats such as buffets alongside tips
OL,11,Fon shortcuts and presentation.
OL,13,FLizzie Haywood, senior trend
OL,14,Finnovation manager at Waitrose, said:
OL,15,F"The '80s was a bold, expressive era
OL,16,Ffor food, and we're seeing that sense
OL,17,Fof fun come back in a big way.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@LO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
