FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781385841
OL,3,CPrawn cocktails and pavlova back on
OL,4,Cmenu as 1980s revival boosts demand
OL,6,F"From prawn cocktails and quiches to
OL,7,Findulgent desserts and standout
OL,8,Fdrinks, people are rediscovering the
OL,9,Fjoy of these classic dishes."
OL,11,FAt Ramsay's newly opened Bread Street
OL,12,FKitchen at London's 22 Bishopsgate,
OL,13,Fhead chef Kamal Rees-John is serving
OL,14,Fpavlova from a dessert trolley.
OL,16,FHe said: "For summer 2026 we're seeing
OL,17,Fa real return to retro '80s classics
OL,18,Fthat feel playful while still
OL,19,Fincorporating elements of finesse and
OL,20,Ftheatre, and pavlova fits perfectly
OL,21,Fwithin that trend.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@]O]xD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781385841
OL,3,CPrawn cocktails and pavlova back on
OL,4,Cmenu as 1980s revival boosts demand
OL,6,F"Our guests are leaning towards
OL,7,Fdesserts that feel joyful, shareable,
OL,8,Fand a little nostalgic, and pavlova
OL,9,Fdelivers all of that."
OL,11,FAs well as 1980s-themed food, the
OL,12,Ffashions of the decade are also having
OL,13,Fa revival.
OL,15,FVogue recently tipped '80s-style
OL,16,Fjewellery as a summer must-have in the
OL,17,Fform of cuffs and hoop earrings, while
OL,18,FMarie Claire cited the '80s-inspired
OL,19,F"Glamoratti aesthetic" as a clothing
OL,20,Ftrend for the summer.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@VO]{D@AOU{D@VO]
